# Busy jobs convention

Read and follow [AGENTS.md](../AGENTS.md) when adding or modifying long-running operations.

- Register every worker with `JobManager` in `src-tauri/src/jobs.rs`
- Never queue or double-run — reject when busy
- UI: use `useJob()` / `JobsProvider`, not local busy `useState`
- No automatic indexing after clone/pull/meta — only the Workspace Index pipeline module
